# Terramate generates these files with LF line endings and fingerprints their
# content to detect manual edits. On Windows, core.autocrlf=true rewrites LF
# to CRLF on checkout, which makes `terramate generate` think the generated
# files were hand-edited ("manually defined code found") and refuse to
# regenerate them. Force LF for all text in this repo so a fresh clone works
# the same on Windows as anywhere else.
* text=auto eol=lf
